{"tid":1980464,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「武漢肺炎」傷害14億人感情 國民黨：台灣許多人看法一樣","createTime":"2020-04-20T06:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T06:58:11.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7e90a230e304af8be62abead9ad3c07dc79c3cf6","tid":1980464,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:09:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3120274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3120274&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=80ed62c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3120274&h=67627fc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3120274</a><br />\n<br />\n記者施曉光／台北報導〕針對「新冠肺炎」疫情，台灣政府迄今仍使用「武漢肺炎」一詞，最近引起國民黨革命實踐研究院院長、台北市議員羅智強質疑是歧視對岸，沒有顧慮14億人的感受。國民黨文傳會主委王育敏今天被媒體問到，這是否代表國民黨的立場？她說，羅智強的質疑有其道理所在，而且國民黨對外也是一律使用「新冠肺炎」。<br />\n<br />\n王育敏說，社會上的確有許多人看法與羅智強一樣，「武漢肺炎」一詞會讓外界認為背後存在抗中的政治思維，況且經WHO定名後，國際間與媒體慣用的名稱就是「新冠肺炎」，羅智強所提出的質疑，有其道理所在，國民黨對外使用名詞也都是「新冠肺炎」。"},{"pid":"6cf3d4eddc9d9aaa4f6bbbb8ffd3c08f029073c7","tid":1980464,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:20:51.000Z","msg":"好啊 中國武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"b50dd70fc532656d0751ade8cec53189704c5095","tid":1980464,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:22:26.000Z","msg":"Noted but no thanks"},{"pid":"6da7a95ceed7a3c9b19b7f7ad892657da820deff","tid":1980464,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:40:44.000Z","msg":"WHO cares<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b379ad21590549c7ddaea53e8a270c82d879bcc","tid":1980464,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:48:19.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"30bf3b3997d9d897eea077fc437be9c6b95431e7","tid":1980464,"